Invoice
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The monthly overview, which lists the payments and withdrawals you have
made using your MasterCard. The invoice overview can take the form of
an account statement, an invoice with a deposit card or an automatic
account deduction via Betalingsservice. Invoices are only printed if
there have been movements on the card account during the period in
MasterCard on mobile phone
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A virtual version of a physical private or
Corporate card. Can be put into a
wallet approved by &BANKNAVN., on a mobile unit such as a smartphone or
tablet.
Afterwards, the virtual payment card on a mobile unit can be used as
contactless payment by means of a wallet when making physical purchases.
