Contactless payment
:SKRSLUT
.br
A card, with built-in antenna, which is connected to the card chip, makes
it possible to make payments without direct contact between the card and
the payment terminal if the payment terminal also has a contactless
device. You can pay simply by holding the card 0-3 centimetres from the
payment terminal's contactless symbol. Cards and payment terminals, that
have the contactless device, will have the symbol - ))) - at the front of
the card or terminal.
.sp 3mm
:FED.
