.br
You must contact Customer Service at Nets as soon as possible if
.br
.of 5mm
-¤you lose your physical card, or
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
-¤your mobile unit with MasterCard on mobile phone, or
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
-¤another person becomes aware of your PIN code, or
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
-¤you realise that your card has been misused, or
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
-¤you suspect that your card has been copied, or
.of
.of 5mm
-¤you otherwise suspect that your card may have been misused.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
