:FED.
YOU MUST CONTACT NETS CUSTOMER SERVICE ON &PBSTLFKUN., THE LINE IS
STAFFED 24/7. STATE YOUR NAME, ADDRESS AND, IF APPROPRIATE, CARD NUMBER AND
ACCOUNT NUMBER OR CIVIL REG. (CPR) NUMBER.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.********
:SKRSLUT.
.********
.kp on
When calling from outside Denmark, use the local number code for
international calls followed by &PBSTLFKUN. (45 is the international
dialling code for Denmark).
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When we have been notified that you have lost your physical card or that
another person knows of your PIN code, the card will be included on a
cancellation list and thus be cancelled via MasterCard s international
authorization system.
The card will also be included on the cancellation list and cancelled if we
have a reasonable suspicion that the card has been misused.
Blocking of your physical card implies that you cannot use your MasterCard
on mobile phone either.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When we are notified that you have lost your mobile unit, your MasterCard
on mobile phone on that specific unit will be blocked.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
This will not influence your physical card directly.
If you suspect that another person has obtained knowledge of your
MasterCard
SecureCode, you are not entitled to cancel the card but to change the code
immediately - this is done on the website of your commercial bank or on
Nets  website. Neither do you need to cancel your card should you have
forgotten your MasterCard SecureCode. Instead, you must create a new code.
