&BANKNAVN. in time, emphasis will be placed on your duty to review
your account movements on a regular basis, see Article 2.5. In any
event, you must contact &BANKNAVN. no later than 13 months after the
sum was withdrawn from your account.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
