5. Processing and disclosure of personal data and information about
purchases etc.
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
5.1. Processing and disclosure of information about name, address, phone
number, civil registration (CPR) number and company registration
(CVR) number
:SKRSLUT.
.br
&BANKNAVN. uses information about name, private address, phone number
and civil registration (CPR) number - for Corporate cards, also
corporate information including company registration (CVR) number - when
issuing cards and in its ongoing administrative processes. The
civil registration (CPR) number can be used in connection with
accessing address information from the Danish Ministry of the
Interior's Central Register of Addresses.
.br
&BANKNAVN. may also use the civil registration (CPR) and/or company
registration (CVR) numbers to provide legally required information to
public authorities about balances on accounts, any interest accrued etc.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
5.2. Processing and disclosure of other information
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The other information that the applicant/company provides, as well as
information collected from bank details, information from credit
information agencies and the like is used by &BANKNAVN. as the basis
for credit assessment on issuing cards, blocking cards and for
ensuring unique identification of the cardholder/company. Such
information is also used as necessary for completing payment
transactions.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
5.3. Consumption data etc.
:SKRSLUT.
.br
When you use your card, a record is made of the card number, the total
transaction sum, the date of the transaction and the location where
the card was used. The payment recipient forwards this information to
&BANKNAVN. via Nets. This information is stored by the payment
recipient, Nets and &BANKNAVN., and it is used in bookkeeping, for
preparing invoices/account statements (including electronic account
statements and allowing the cardholder to view his/her consumption via
the Internet), and for subsequently correcting any errors.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
The information mentioned above is only otherwise disclosed in
cases where such is required by law and/or in legal proceedings
related to claims arising from use of the card. In the case of
corporate cards, this information may be processed and disclosed to
the company to allow the company itself to process the data in
various management information systems.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
5.4. Storage of information
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Personal information including any information collected concerning
liquidity and information about purchases is stored by &BANKNAVN. and
is physically present at the &BANKNAVN. data centre.
.br
This information is stored for as long as the cardholder/company has a
MasterCard card issued by &BANKNAVN..
.kp off
.sp 3mm
.kp on
Information about purchases may be deleted after five years. On
termination of the customer relationship, the information will be
retained for as long as may be necessary for disclosure to public
authorities, if required.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
When registering for MasterCard SecureCode, your mobile phone number will
be stored by Nets and used to send out one-off codes.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
